00:32:50.278 --> 00:32:53.855
fail to coordinate;
and (0,0) here if they fail to

00:32:53.855 --> 00:32:58.000
coordinate;
and (1,2), (1,2) here.

00:32:58.000 --> 00:33:02.892
So the implication of this is
that Player 2 who we'll assume

00:33:02.892 --> 00:33:08.033
is David, so David would like to
