Professor Ben Polak:

00:34:12.833 --> 00:34:13.990
You're going to go to China
and Nina?

00:34:13.990 --> 00:34:15.603
Student: I chose S.
Professor Ben Polak:

00:34:15.603 --> 00:34:17.860
Great, so they managed to
