00:58:00.241 --> 00:58:02.162
question, and some of you may
decide you don't want to

00:58:02.162 --> 00:58:03.829
interview with Morgan Stanley or
McKinsey,

00:58:03.829 --> 00:58:07.704
you might want to interview
with some accounting firm when

00:58:07.704 --> 00:58:10.699
you leave Yale.
God forbid, but you might.

00:58:10.699 --> 00:58:14.257
So let's have a look at how the
accountants would answer this

00:58:14.257 --> 00:58:16.450
question.
So I think the accountants

00:58:16.450 --> 00:58:20.255
would do this.
They would say--but before we

00:58:20.255 --> 00:58:24.706
